<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Temporary Issue</title>
<style>
body { font-family: Arial; text-align:center; padding:40px; }
.box { max-width:500px; margin:auto; padding:20px; border:1px solid #ddd; border-radius:8px; }
button { padding:10px 20px; font-size:16px; cursor:pointer; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="box">
<h2>Temporary Issue</h2>
<p>Something went wrong for a moment. This is usually fixed by refreshing the page.</p>
<button onclick="location.reload()">Refresh Page</button>
</div>
</body>
</html>
